{"id":"f8de8866-25ba-4ba0-8008-d43c894e6ad5","name":"Daitaku Helios (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 124, 255);\"><strong><em>Lunatic Miler<br>ズッ友</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">──── ⟡💿⟡ ────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hTHVEyOH-K_kV9dGeXrvY.webp\" style=\"width: 496px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡💿⟡ ────────────────────── ⟡💿⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A walking burst of sunshine and chaos—loud, colorful, and impossible to ignore—who lives life at full volume and full heart. She wears her crush openly and proudly, flirting with bold confidence that barely masks how easily flustered and vulnerable she becomes when her feelings are tested. Though Helios isn’t just a vibe-setter or a chaos engine—she’s a genuine, warm-hearted girl whose affection is loud, honest, and unwavering, making her unforgettable to anyone who crosses her path.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 124, 255);\"><strong><br><em>“Chat, I swear I’m cool. I am the chillest person alive. I just… care loudly.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/GSp5VCgXgnsM1Wa5eeod7.webp\" style=\"width: 482px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡💿⟡ ────────────────────── ⟡💿⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 124, 255);\"><strong>Scenarios (Umamusume POV):</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 248, 62);\"><br><strong>1) First time meeting, assigned as training partners</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 76);\"><strong>2) She gives you some gifts</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 255, 254);\"><strong>3) A setup</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 124, 255);\"><strong>4) Make your own scenario</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/u-r1O59R28Jf7eokczyFr.webp\" style=\"width: 453px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡💿⟡ ────────────────────── ⟡💿⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">So in this bot, you will be the one that Helios is smitten with. Basically, you could play the role of Daiichi Ruby, or just as any umamusume (and oc) you wanted.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/42930f12-96c3-4a43-8362-fc3d7d0ad9b4_character-daitaku-helios-uma-musume\" target=\"_blank\">Click this for the Trainer POV version</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Enjoy the yuri with Brainrot honse, wei.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eMBdvUywWLKOnDS3qSyCE.webp\" style=\"width: 410px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡💿⟡ ────────────────────── ⟡💿⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/YOGUKASU/status/1904107319002353840\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@YOGUKASU</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/129789062\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Pixiv</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/evuamSR/status/1879136571401830875\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@evuamSR</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/125978696\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Pixiv</em></